title: Tammy Tell Me True [1961 - USA] (Sandra Dee) comedy
description:
Tammy Tell Me True (1961 - USA)

Comedy

starring . . . . Sandra Dee, John Gavin, Charles Drake
 
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0055503/


In this emotional romance, the young backwoods girl Tammy lives in a houseboat on the river. She is very sad because she hasn't heard from her college-student boyfriend in ages. Determined to be near him, she cruises her boat down to his university and enrolls. To pay expenses she gets a job. Her new boss is pleased and ends up borrowing Tammy's boat for a short vacation. Tammy soon finds herself pursued by a handsome professor.
